{"tid":1254384,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"Telegram更新有類似FireChat功能","createTime":"2019-06-24T05:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T14:42:52.000Z","uid":32901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"af6a02cdb9117fb352366bf4eb12f1de4355671d","tid":1254384,"uid":32901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:55:15.000Z","msg":"Adding to Contacts Made Easier<br />\n&bull; You can now add any users to your contacts, even if their phone numbers are not visible. <br />\n&bull; Quickly add users standing next to you by opening Contacts &gt; Add People Nearby. You will see people who have this section open.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Location-Based Chats<br />\n&bull; Host local communities by creating location-based group chats from the People Nearby section.</span><br />\n<br />\nTransfer Group Chats<br />\n&bull; Transfer ownership of group chats and channels by granting full rights to another admin. Useful when switching jobs or if you just want to retire as creator.<br />\n<br />\nAnd More<br />\n&bull; Use Siri shortcuts to open chats with people.<br />\n&bull; Choose app icon style and enjoy new theme previews in Appearance settings.<br />\n&bull; Toggle message previews for specific chats, and use Search and &lsquo;Delete All&rsquo; tools in Notification Exceptions.<br />\n<br />\nMore about this update:<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegram.org/blog/contacts-local-groups\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.org%2Fblog%2Fcontacts-local-groups&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=661bba0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.org/blog/contacts-local-groups</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ge5t9zd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGe5t9zd.png&h=7830a627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c948abb748dee0ab61c1eee9dbf487d6e79ab64","tid":1254384,"uid":32901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:55:43.000Z","msg":"大家快啲update<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0355effd43d8e1f9a78d9cef84fefad3f30cfb8","tid":1254384,"uid":32901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:56:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b0e7595e495fdee30c25dc7be68abbff8e02ec7f","tid":1254384,"uid":32901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:56:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f7f54ff7d421914073bde5bc263ab7e7c5643195","tid":1254384,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:58:53.000Z","msg":"[麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以經登記咗都要去查下啲資料啱唔啱</span></strong><br />\n好多人都話冇咗選民記錄 大家都要check下 <br />\n個server會on99咁好慢 凌晨時份會好啲 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fcheckvrstatus.htm&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=b8a58027\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm</a><br />\n或者打電話28911001 &gt; 1 &gt; 2去查 扮工時間9-6<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新登記</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=746440ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=